        "range": "Self.",
        "overview": {
          "base": "You gain a benefit that you can expend in one of following ways of your choosing.\n<dl><dt>Attack Combo</dt>\n<dd>The next @L[Category:Attack abilities]{attack} you make is @L[Keyword:AV0]{AV0}.</dd>\n<dt>Check Combo</dt>\n<dd>The next time you @L[Ability:Attempt Check]{Attempt Check} you do so with @L[Core:Advantage]{advantage}.</dd></dl>\nYou may only choose one benefit per use of Combo.",
          "proficient": "The list of possible benefits you can choose from is expanded to include the following.\n<dl><dt>Block Combo</dt>\n<dd>The next @L[Category:Block abilities]{block} you make may be done with <i>2</i> @L[Category:Equipment]{items} instead of 1. You add the @L[Core:Block Interaction]{BV} for both.</dd>\n<dt>Condition Combo</dt>\n<dd>Instead of rolling [[/roll 2d4]] to end some @L[Category:Effects]{effect}, you may roll either [[/roll 1d4]] or [[/roll 3d4]] (you choose). The effect ends if any of the dice roll a 4.</dd>\n<dt>Feat Combo</dt>\n<dd>The next time you make a @L[Category:Feat abilities]{feat save}, you do so with @L[Core:Advantage]{advantage}.</dd>\n<dt>Resistance Combo</dt>\n<dd>The next time you make a @L[Category:Resistance effects]{resistance save}, you do so with @L[Core:Advantage]{advantage}.</dd></dl>",
